T1  - Redescription of Mesochaetopterus selangolus (Polychaeta: Chaetopteridae), Based on Type Specimens and Recently Collected Material from Morib Beach, Malaysia
JO  - Pac Sci
SN  - 0030-8870
VL  - 53
